data.description: Step into this home that offers a perfect blend of elegance and practicality.   The kitchen , a chef's delight, along with the formal dining room and family room is a space ideal for cooking or social gatherings. The first floor also features a bedroom with its own full bathroom.  Second floor consists of bamboo flooring throughout the bedrooms along with a great loft space.  Outside, an above-ground pool is surrounded by lush landscaping. A shed and a well-fed sprinkler system enhance outdoor utility.  Newer A/C units (2021) along with the home’s impact windows and doors add safety and energy efficiency.  This property is a haven for those seeking a blend of Miami’s lifestyle with the tranquility of a well-appointed home. Experience the best of both worlds in this remarkable residence.
